{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"It's a great honor to be here."},{"time":3000,"text":"It's a great honor to be here talking about cities,"},{"time":5000,"text":"talking about the future of cities."},{"time":8000,"text":"It's great to be here as a mayor."},{"time":10000,"text":"I really do believe that mayors have the political position"},{"time":13000,"text":"to really change people's lives."},{"time":16000,"text":"That's the place to be."},{"time":18000,"text":"And it's great to be here as the mayor of Rio."},{"time":21000,"text":"Rio's a beautiful city,"},{"time":23000,"text":"a vibrant place, special place."},{"time":25000,"text":"Actually, you're looking at a guy"},{"time":27000,"text":"who has the best job in the world."},{"time":29000,"text":"And I really wanted to share with you"},{"time":31000,"text":"a very special moment of my life"},{"time":33000,"text":"and the history of the city of Rio."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35000,"text":"(Video) Announcer: And now, ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":38000,"text":"the envelope containing the result."},{"time":40000,"text":"Jacques Rogge: I have the honor to announce"},{"time":42000,"text":"that the games of the 31st Olympiad"},{"time":45000,"text":"are awarded to the city of Rio de Janeiro."},{"time":49000,"text":"(Cheering)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"EP: Okay, that's very touching, very emotional,"},{"time":58000,"text":"but it was not easy to get there."},{"time":60000,"text":"Actually it was a very hard challenge."},{"time":63000,"text":"We had to beat the European monarchy."},{"time":66000,"text":"This is Juan Carlos, king of Spain."},{"time":69000,"text":"We had to beat the powerful Japanese with all of their technology."},{"time":72000,"text":"We had to beat the most powerful man in the world"},{"time":75000,"text":"defending his own city."},{"time":78000,"text":"So it was not easy at all."},{"time":80000,"text":"And actually this last guy here said a phrase a few years ago"},{"time":83000,"text":"that I think fits perfectly to the situation"},{"time":86000,"text":"of Rio winning the Olympic bid."},{"time":88000,"text":"We really showed that, yes, we can."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92000,"text":"And really, this is the reason I came here tonight."},{"time":94000,"text":"I came here tonight to tell you"},{"time":96000,"text":"that things can be done,"},{"time":98000,"text":"that you don't have always to be rich or powerful"},{"time":101000,"text":"to get things on the way,"},{"time":103000,"text":"that cities are a great challenge."},{"time":106000,"text":"It's a difficult task to deal with cities."},{"time":108000,"text":"But with some original ways"},{"time":110000,"text":"of getting things done,"},{"time":112000,"text":"with some basic commandments,"},{"time":114000,"text":"you can really get cities"},{"time":116000,"text":"to be a great, great place to live."},{"time":119000,"text":"I want you all to imagine Rio."},{"time":121000,"text":"You probably think about a city full of energy,"},{"time":124000,"text":"a vibrant city full of green."},{"time":126000,"text":"And nobody showed that better"},{"time":128000,"text":"than Carlos Saldanha in last year's \"Rio.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":130000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":138000,"text":"(Video) Bird: This is incredible."},{"time":140000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":152000,"text":"EP: Okay, some parts of Rio are pretty much like that,"},{"time":154000,"text":"but it's not like that everywhere."},{"time":157000,"text":"We're like every big city in the world."},{"time":159000,"text":"We've got lots of people,"},{"time":161000,"text":"pollution, cars, concrete, lots of concrete."},{"time":164000,"text":"These pictures I'm showing here,"},{"time":166000,"text":"they are some pictures from Madureira."},{"time":168000,"text":"It's like the heart of the suburb in Rio."},{"time":170000,"text":"And I want to use an example of Rio"},{"time":172000,"text":"that we're doing in Madureira, in this region,"},{"time":174000,"text":"to see what we should think as our first commandment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"So every time you see a concrete jungle like that,"},{"time":180000,"text":"what you've got to do is find open spaces."},{"time":183000,"text":"If you don't have open spaces,"},{"time":185000,"text":"you've got to go there and open spaces."},{"time":187000,"text":"So go inside these open spaces"},{"time":189000,"text":"and make it that people can get inside"},{"time":191000,"text":"and use those spaces."},{"time":193000,"text":"This is going to be the third largest park in Rio"},{"time":196000,"text":"by June this year."},{"time":198000,"text":"It's going to be a place where people can meet,"},{"time":200000,"text":"where you can put nature."},{"time":202000,"text":"The temperature's going to drop two, three degrees centigrade."},{"time":205000,"text":"So the first commandment"},{"time":207000,"text":"I want to leave you tonight"},{"time":209000,"text":"is, a city of the future"},{"time":212000,"text":"has to be environmentally friendly."},{"time":215000,"text":"Every time you think of a city,"},{"time":217000,"text":"you've got to think green."},{"time":219000,"text":"You've got to think green and green."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222000,"text":"So moving to our second commandment that I wanted to show you."},{"time":225000,"text":"Let's think that cities are made of people,"},{"time":227000,"text":"lots of people together."},{"time":229000,"text":"cities are packed with people."},{"time":231000,"text":"So how do you move these people around?"},{"time":234000,"text":"When you have 3.5 billion people living in cities --"},{"time":237000,"text":"by 2050, it's going to be 6 billion people."},{"time":240000,"text":"So every time you think about moving these people around,"},{"time":242000,"text":"you think about high-capacity transportation."},{"time":245000,"text":"But there is a problem."},{"time":247000,"text":"High-capacity transportation means"},{"time":249000,"text":"spending lots and lots of money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"So what I'm going to show here"},{"time":254000,"text":"is something that was already presented in TED"},{"time":256000,"text":"by the former mayor of Curitiba"},{"time":258000,"text":"who created that, a city in Brazil, Jaime Lerner."},{"time":261000,"text":"And it's something that we're doing, again, lots in Rio."},{"time":264000,"text":"It's the BRT, the Bus Rapid Transit."},{"time":266000,"text":"So you get a bus. It's a simple bus that everybody knows."},{"time":269000,"text":"You transform it inside as a train car."},{"time":272000,"text":"You use separate lanes, dedicated lanes."},{"time":275000,"text":"The contractors, they don't like that."},{"time":277000,"text":"You don't have to dig deep down underground."},{"time":280000,"text":"You can build nice stations."},{"time":282000,"text":"This is actually a station that we're doing in Rio."},{"time":285000,"text":"Again, you don't have to dig deep down underground"},{"time":287000,"text":"to make a station like that."},{"time":289000,"text":"This station has the same comfort, the same features"},{"time":292000,"text":"as a subway station."},{"time":294000,"text":"A kilometer of this costs a tenth of a subway."},{"time":297000,"text":"So spending much less money and doing it much faster,"},{"time":300000,"text":"you can really change the way people move."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302000,"text":"This is a map of Rio."},{"time":304000,"text":"All the lines, the colored lines you see there,"},{"time":307000,"text":"it's our high-capacity transportation network."},{"time":310000,"text":"In this present time today,"},{"time":312000,"text":"we only carry 18 percent of our population"},{"time":315000,"text":"in high-capacity transportation."},{"time":317000,"text":"With the BRTs we're doing,"},{"time":319000,"text":"again, the cheapest and fastest way,"},{"time":322000,"text":"we're going to move to 63 percent of the population"},{"time":326000,"text":"being carried by high-capacity transportation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328000,"text":"So remember what I said:"},{"time":330000,"text":"You don't always have to be rich or powerful"},{"time":332000,"text":"to get things done."},{"time":334000,"text":"You can find original ways to get things done."},{"time":337000,"text":"So the second commandment I want to leave you tonight"},{"time":339000,"text":"is, a city of the future"},{"time":341000,"text":"has to deal with mobility and integration"},{"time":344000,"text":"of its people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"Moving to the third commandment."},{"time":350000,"text":"And this is the most controversial one."},{"time":352000,"text":"It has to do with the favelas, the slums --"},{"time":355000,"text":"whatever you call it, there are different names all over the world."},{"time":358000,"text":"But the point we want to make here tonight"},{"time":360000,"text":"is, favelas are not always a problem."},{"time":364000,"text":"I mean, favelas can sometimes"},{"time":367000,"text":"really be a solution,"},{"time":369000,"text":"if you deal with them,"},{"time":371000,"text":"if you put public policy inside the favelas."},{"time":373000,"text":"Let me just show a map of Rio again."},{"time":375000,"text":"Rio has 6.3 million inhabitants --"},{"time":378000,"text":"More than 20 percent, 1.4 million, live in the favelas."},{"time":382000,"text":"All these red parts are favelas."},{"time":384000,"text":"So you see, they are spread all over the city."},{"time":387000,"text":"This is a typical view of a favela in Rio."},{"time":390000,"text":"You see the contrast between the rich and poor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393000,"text":"So I want to make two points here tonight about favelas."},{"time":396000,"text":"The first one is,"},{"time":398000,"text":"you can change from what I call a [vicious] circle"},{"time":400000,"text":"to a virtual circle."},{"time":402000,"text":"But what you've got to do to get that"},{"time":404000,"text":"is you've got to go inside the favelas,"},{"time":407000,"text":"bring in the basic services --"},{"time":409000,"text":"mainly education and health -- with high quality."},{"time":412000,"text":"I'm going to give a fast example here."},{"time":414000,"text":"This was an old building in a favela in Rio --"},{"time":416000,"text":"[unclear favela name] --"},{"time":418000,"text":"that we just transformed into a primary school,"},{"time":421000,"text":"with high quality."},{"time":424000,"text":"This is primary assistance in health"},{"time":426000,"text":"that we built inside a favela,"},{"time":428000,"text":"again, with high quality."},{"time":430000,"text":"We call it a family clinic."},{"time":432000,"text":"So the first point is bring basic services"},{"time":434000,"text":"inside the favelas"},{"time":436000,"text":"with high quality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438000,"text":"The second point I want to make about the favelas"},{"time":440000,"text":"is, you've got to open spaces in the favela."},{"time":442000,"text":"Bring infrastructure"},{"time":444000,"text":"to the favelas, to the slums, wherever you are."},{"time":447000,"text":"Rio has the aim, by 2020,"},{"time":449000,"text":"to have all its favelas completely urbanized."},{"time":452000,"text":"Another example, this was completely packed with houses,"},{"time":455000,"text":"and then we built this, what we call, a knowledge square."},{"time":458000,"text":"This is a place with high technology"},{"time":460000,"text":"where the kids that live in a poor house next to this place"},{"time":463000,"text":"can go inside and have access to all technology."},{"time":466000,"text":"We even built a theater there -- 3D movie."},{"time":469000,"text":"And this is the kind of change you can get for that."},{"time":473000,"text":"And by the end of the day you get something better than a TED Prize,"},{"time":476000,"text":"which is this great laugh"},{"time":478000,"text":"from a kid that lives in the favela."},{"time":480000,"text":"So the third commandment I want to leave here tonight"},{"time":483000,"text":"is, a city of the future"},{"time":486000,"text":"has to be socially integrated."},{"time":488000,"text":"You cannot deal with a city"},{"time":490000,"text":"if it's not socially integrated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":492000,"text":"But moving to our fourth commandment,"},{"time":496000,"text":"I really wouldn't be here tonight."},{"time":498000,"text":"Between November and May, Rio's completely packed."},{"time":503000,"text":"We just had last week Carnivale."},{"time":505000,"text":"It was great. It was lots of fun."},{"time":507000,"text":"We have New Year's Eve."},{"time":509000,"text":"There's like two million people on Copacabana Beach."},{"time":511000,"text":"We have problems."},{"time":513000,"text":"We fight floods, tropical rains at this time of the year."},{"time":516000,"text":"You can imagine how people get happy with me"},{"time":518000,"text":"watching these kinds of scenes."},{"time":520000,"text":"We have problems with the tropical rains."},{"time":523000,"text":"Almost every year"},{"time":525000,"text":"we have these landslides, which are terrible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527000,"text":"But the reason I could come here"},{"time":529000,"text":"is because of that."},{"time":531000,"text":"This was something we did with IBM"},{"time":534000,"text":"that's a little bit more than a year old."},{"time":536000,"text":"It's what we call the Operations Center of Rio."},{"time":539000,"text":"And I wanted to show that I can govern my city, using technology,"},{"time":542000,"text":"from here, from Long Beach,"},{"time":544000,"text":"so I got here last night and I know everything."},{"time":546000,"text":"We're going to speak now to the Operations Center."},{"time":548000,"text":"This is Osorio,"},{"time":550000,"text":"he's our secretary of urban affairs."},{"time":552000,"text":"So Osorio, good to be there with you."},{"time":555000,"text":"I've already told the people"},{"time":557000,"text":"that we have tropical rain this time of year."},{"time":560000,"text":"So how's the weather in Rio now?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":562000,"text":"Osorio: The weather is fine. We have fair weather today."},{"time":565000,"text":"Let me get you our weather satellite radar."},{"time":568000,"text":"You see just a little bit of moisture around the city."},{"time":571000,"text":"Absolutely no problem in the city in terms of weather,"},{"time":575000,"text":"today and in the next few days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577000,"text":"EP: Okay, how's the traffic?"},{"time":579000,"text":"We, at this time of year, get lots of traffic jams."},{"time":581000,"text":"People get mad at the mayor. So how's the traffic tonight?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":584000,"text":"Osario: Well traffic tonight is fine."},{"time":586000,"text":"Let me get you one of our 8,000 buses."},{"time":590000,"text":"A live transmission in downtown Rio for you, Mr. Mayor."},{"time":593000,"text":"You see, the streets are clear."},{"time":595000,"text":"Now it's 11:00 pm in Rio."},{"time":598000,"text":"Nothing of concern in terms of traffic."},{"time":600000,"text":"I'll get to you now the incidents of the day."},{"time":603000,"text":"We had heavy traffic early in the morning"},{"time":606000,"text":"and in the rush hour in the afternoon,"},{"time":608000,"text":"but nothing of big concern."},{"time":610000,"text":"We are below average"},{"time":612000,"text":"in terms of traffic incidents in the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":614000,"text":"EP: Okay, so you're showing now some public services."},{"time":616000,"text":"These are the cars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":618000,"text":"Osorio: Absolutely, Mr. Mayor."},{"time":620000,"text":"Let me get you the fleet of our waste collection trucks."},{"time":623000,"text":"This is live transmission."},{"time":625000,"text":"We have GPS's in all of our trucks."},{"time":627000,"text":"And you can see them working"},{"time":629000,"text":"in all parts of the city."},{"time":631000,"text":"Waste collection on time."},{"time":633000,"text":"Public services working well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":635000,"text":"EP: Okay, Osorio, thank you very much."},{"time":637000,"text":"It was great to have you here."},{"time":639000,"text":"We're going to move so that I can make a conclusion."},{"time":641000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":644000,"text":"Okay, so no files, this place, no paperwork,"},{"time":648000,"text":"no distance, 24/7 working."},{"time":651000,"text":"So the fourth commandment I want to share with you here tonight"},{"time":654000,"text":"is, a city of the future"},{"time":656000,"text":"has to use technology to be present."},{"time":658000,"text":"I don't need to be there anymore to know and to administrate the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661000,"text":"But everything that I said here tonight, or the commandments,"},{"time":664000,"text":"are means, are ways,"},{"time":666000,"text":"for us to govern cities --"},{"time":669000,"text":"invest in infrastructure, invest in the green,"},{"time":671000,"text":"open parks, open spaces,"},{"time":673000,"text":"integrate socially, use technology."},{"time":676000,"text":"But at the end of the day, when we talk about cities,"},{"time":679000,"text":"we talk about a gathering of people."},{"time":681000,"text":"And we cannot see that as a problem."},{"time":683000,"text":"That is fantastic."},{"time":685000,"text":"If there's 3.5 billion now,"},{"time":687000,"text":"it's going to be six billion then it's going to be 10 billion."},{"time":689000,"text":"That is great, that means we're going to have"},{"time":692000,"text":"10 billion minds working together,"},{"time":694000,"text":"10 billion talents together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":697000,"text":"So a city of the future,"},{"time":699000,"text":"I really do believe"},{"time":701000,"text":"that it's a city that cares about its citizens,"},{"time":704000,"text":"integrates socially its citizens."},{"time":706000,"text":"A city of the future is a city that can never let anyone out"},{"time":709000,"text":"of this great party, which are cities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}